kernel:
OUT(^welcome to PyComp OS^)
VAR program
READ count_ten
MOV program REG:-1
EXEC program
END
count_ten:
OUT(^This program counts by 1 from 0 to 10 and then stops^)
VAR counter (0)
out(^counter:^)
LABEL count_to_ten
ADD [counter] (1)
MOV counter REG:-1
out(^counter:^)
out(counter)
CMP [counter] (10)
JE <ending>
JMP <count_to_ten>
LABEL ending
END
